What is Energy & U?
Welcome to "Energy and U!" Brought to life by top minds from the University of Minnesota, and enriched with the generous support of the National Science Foundation, this program is ready to light up the Valley. A fun-filled exploration of energy for young learners, "Energy and U" is all about inspiring the next generation to care for our wonderful planet. It's time to power up your curiosity and spark our sense of responsibility. Join us in the adventure!
